{"tid":1351692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣請入］［理性］真正嘅網軍係想我地出黎打生打死","createTime":"2019-07-22T16:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T06:39:01.000Z","uid":183891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1038d746c2a3397673ce05056cecb5602ed15390","tid":1351692,"uid":183891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:06:23.000Z","msg":"呢兩日係香港最撚黑暗嘅日子<br />\n<br />\n但係大家係不斷唸點撚樣報仇 打鳩d狗同鄉黑 嘅同時<br />\n<br />\n有冇唸過點樣做到對<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">實體經濟嘅最大衝擊</span><br />\n<br />\n唔係你禮拜日唔洗翻工出黎同佢地隻抽 群毆 <br />\n第二日再擔驚受怕咁翻工放工<br />\n<br />\n而係切切實實咁發動一個癱瘓交通行動 阻止d人翻工 癱瘓實體經濟<br />\n<br />\n將我地自己嘅人命傷亡降到最低嘅同時<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">強逼政府回應每一件事</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbe water講嘅係以最細嘅力 去克最大嘅力<br />\n<br />\n唔係慢慢等我地嘅手足打傷打殘抖抖再黎過咁樣無休止呀<br />\n<br />\n打死一個黑警 除左爽 根本動搖唔到呢個政權嘅分毫<br />\n<br />\n更何況而家武力上佔優勢嘅一係狗 二係黑 三先係我地呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">醒啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係不合作運動呀</span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"995762fc9dc7f68dd2edd902538f09fa701e6088","tid":1351692,"uid":266736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:39:01.000Z","msg":"[西班牙文宣組]<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/GWuZfEjL__AGorUyyqyPKQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FGWuZfEjL__AGorUyyqyPKQ&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=e8f9a94c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/GWuZfEjL__AGorUyyqyPKQ</a><br />\n識西班文既朋友入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}